In this case, the goal is to balance a feeder load profile. If a load serving entity (LSE) can control its hourly consumption precisely, the LSE can bid a baseline load, PfBaseline\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
